data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom / 3 bath home in the sought after Lambert High, Riverwatch Middle and Settles Bridge Elementary School district.      Located on a cul-de-sac, this home offers a large Primary Suite with additional 2 bedrooms and full bath on the main level.  Additional, completely private guest suite area with a closet and full bath is on the second level.     Fully framed basement with all electrical in place, HVAC, and stubbed for bath. The basement could easily be finished as an additional family space/suite or rented. No rental restrictions.     Large .39 acre cul-de-sac lot with large and private fenced in backyard Ca facing the woods.     Roof - 2 years old, Water Heater - 2 years old, new premium exterior paint 2022, HVAC replaced in 2018.  Replaced/rebuilt the interior chimney and supports to higher quality in 2022.  Many other maintenance updates.  New carpet in primary bedroom and upper level. New range. New larger gutters and french drain installed, Summer 2022.     Riverbrooke offers 3 tennis courts, a full-size basketball court, a playground, a kiddie pool with fountains, a splash pad with many fun features, full-size pool with on-site monitors, and nature trails.
